  <section class="content">
    <h2>Purpose</h2>
    <p>
      Global Infrastructure Advisory exists to strengthen the way governments, donors, and organizations plan, procure,
      deliver, and oversee infrastructure. Our mission is to bring engineering‑minded discipline, transparent governance,
      and modern automation to the world’s most critical projects.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Integrity in Procurement:</strong> Ensuring fairness, compliance, and accountability.</li>
      <li><strong>Engineering Precision:</strong> Applying technical rigor to planning and oversight.</li>
      <li><strong>AI‑Driven Insight:</strong> Using automation and dashboards to improve decision‑making.</li>
      <li><strong>Global Impact:</strong> Supporting infrastructure programs across continents and sectors.</li>
      <li><strong>Capacity Building:</strong> Empowering institutions with tools, templates, and training.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Long‑Term Vision</h2>
    <p>
      This platform is designed to grow over time — evolving into a self‑running ecosystem that supports job creation,
      workforce development, PMO maturity, and infrastructure transparency. With Azure‑ready architecture and AI
      automation already embedded, the mission extends far beyond consulting: it is about building systems that sustain
